Dplyr row slice for chronogram

dplyr_row_slice.cg_tbl.Rd

As recommended here: https://dplyr.tidyverse.org/reference/dplyr_extending.html

Usage

# S3 method for class 'cg_tbl'
dplyr_row_slice(data, i, ...)

Arguments

data

data

i

rows to eg slice

...

additional arguments

Value

a cg_tbl after a dplyr verb action

Details

Ensures dplyr verbs return a cg_tbl, rather than tbl. User can ignore.
